Class Quadtree

java.lang.Object
  Quadtree
Direct Known Subclasses:
Octree
public class Quadtree
extends java.lang.Object

The Quadtree class defines a two dimensional binary tree. Each node references a quadrant. The root node references a quadrant that encompasses all other sub-quadrants.

Author:
Christopher Glasz
